    <item>
      <title>信用交易者由华尔街的白关节骑行而震撼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/credit-traders-jolted-awake-by-wall-street-s-white-knuckle-ride</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国公司债券市场中，人们通过股票和其他风险资产的恐惧逐渐流血，这引起了新的担忧，这些债务在过去两年中累积的债务可能要进行更正。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/credit-traders-jolted-awake-by-wall-street-s-white-knuckle-ride</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 23:08:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场的投机边缘被炸毁了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/market-s-speculative-fringe-is-blasted-as-equity-rout-snowballs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国股票中发生风险的飞行对去年大赢家的科技巨头来说是痛苦的，但与在市场上更具投机性边缘的偏差相比，这显得苍白。]]></description>
